<emphasis id="3ACC0B44FFB5FFB0FE93FD12FCC034D1" bold="true" box="[349,775,712,733]" pageId="1" pageNumber="414">
Key to Genera of Neotropical 
<taxonomicName id="CFB8ACD5FFB5FFB0FD57FD12FCC034D1" box="[665,775,712,733]" class="Insecta" family="Dryophthoridae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="414" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Litosomini">Litosomini</taxonomicName>
